---
import { MessageCircle, Heart } from "@lucide/astro";
---
<div class="bg-pink-700 text-white py-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      {/* Content */}
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div
            class="inline-block bg-white/20 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium"
          >
            Clínica Especializada
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
            Sobre DeltaScan
          </h1>
        </div>

        <p class="text-lg text-pink-100 leading-relaxed">
          En DeltaScan realizamos estudios de imágenes con un enfoque claro:
          tratarte con respeto, explicarte cada paso y ofrecer resultados
          confiables.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/hacer-cita"
            class="bg-white text-pink-700 hover:bg-pink-50 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-colors"
          >
            <MessageCircle class="w-5 h-5" />
            Agenda tu cita
        </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Image */}
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <div class="relative">
          <div
            class="w-80 h-96 bg-white/20 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl"
          >
            <img
              src="/sobre-nosotros/doctoresradiologos.webp"
              alt="Doctores Radiólogos de la clínica DeltaScan"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 bg-white text-pink-700 p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg"
          >
            <Heart class="w-8 h-8" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
